#[self_referencing]
struct EvenWalkMapIterator<TCurve, TMapFn, TResult>
where
    TCurve: 'static + BezierCurve,
    TMapFn: for<'a> Fn(CurveSection<'a, TCurve>) -> TResult,
{
    curve: TCurve,
    map_fn: TMapFn,

    #[borrows(curve)]
    #[not_covariant]
    walk_iterator: EvenWalkIterator<'this, TCurve>,
}
